description.en:
LunarSwap is an innovative project, all of your Lunar tokens will be automatically staked for you to be rewarded in BNB and LunarSwap tokens!

Our ecosystem will consist of the following:
- Pending orders for DEX trading: No more sleepless nights with PancakeSwap. Set limits for Take Profit, Stop Loss, and Entries
- Lunar sniper: Automatic bot to secure your entry spot upon listing
- LunarSwap platform: LunarSwap’s very own swap platform based on PancakeSwap Liquidity
